—and </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">that somehow we have </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">to meet that growth of demand.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 12pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">The </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">proposition </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">I </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">want to open with is t</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">hat it is not just about totals; it</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt"> is al</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">so about who is in that demand and </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">what </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">is </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">the </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">changing nature of </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">the </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">demand that is going to be placed upon </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">the </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">system in </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">the </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">projected period to 2020 that NHS England </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">are</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt"> now </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">talking about.</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">I </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">would be grateful if you could tell </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">the </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">Committe